name: TradeForex.com
overview:
TradeForex.com is an online learning resource to educate people on how to trade currency online. The website provides a wide base of subjects and covers everything from basic to advanced concepts.

along with the educational resources the website also provide valuable tools that the use can access to help with Forex trading. These tools include live FX charts with all of the major currency pairs and information about commodity trading.

In addition, TradeForex.com is looking to expand their product offering by adding a social aspect to the website. With forums and chats users will be able to connect and share Forex trading insights and issues.
